.Dd March 12, 2024
.Dt APPJAIL-USAGE 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm appjail-usage
.Nd Display the syntax of a given command
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm appjail usage
.Ar command
.Sh DESCRIPTION
Shows the syntax of the given
.Em command "."
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Ex -std "appjail usage"
It may fail for one of the following reasons:
.Pp
.Bl -dash -compact
.It
.Em EX_USAGE ":"
The
.Em command
was not specified.
.It
.Em EX_NOINPUT ":"
The
.Em command
does not exist.
.It
.Em EX_SOFTWARE ":"
The function responsible for displaying the usage message is not
implemented.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr appjail 1
.Xr appjail-help 1
.Xr sysexits 3
